---
title: Cheesy BBQ Smashed Chickpea Enchiladas with Caramelised Onion & BBQ Mayo
description: With wholesome chickpeas, mini flour tortillas, gooey Cheddar cheese and sweet caramelised onion, this fan favourite dish style
is colourful, delicious and a heap of fun. Don’t forget to dollop on the smokey BBQ mayo to really get the party started!
